# QX mod (this Git repository)

- **`VERSION`** (semver, one line) must match **`mod_version`** in root **`gradle.properties`**.
- On meaningful changes: update **`CHANGELOG.md`**, bump **`VERSION`** / **`mod_version`**, **commit**, **`git push`**, annotated tag **`vX.Y.Z`**, **`git push origin vX.Y.Z`**.
- **`.github/workflows/`** — CI runs **`./gradlew build`** (NeoForge userdev); artifact **`build/libs/*-neoforge-*.jar`**. On tag **`v*`**, release attaches that JAR. **Swap** + reduced Gradle heap on the runner when needed.
